## Contributing Examples

When adding new examples:

1. **Choose representative scenarios** - Cover common use cases and edge cases
2. **Show complete context** - Include full input and output
3. **Explain the "why"** - Help readers understand the reasoning
4. **Keep them current** - Update examples when the skill changes

**Example Template:**

```markdown
## Example N: [Title]

**Scenario:** [One-line description]

**Input:**
```
[Input]
```

**Expected Output:**
```
[Output]
```

**Explanation:** [Why this is the correct result]
```
